Now, they have to find out what happened to him and what happened to the one million dollars that he had on his ship.

Episodes.Plot: A decomposed body is discovered in a tub of acid at a naval base and Ducky and Abby learn that the victim was a submariner. With this new information, the team must find out which sub the man posing as the victim is in and what intentions he may have towards the sub.
